query: WITH entities AS (SELECT external_id, id FROM cala_account_sets WHERE COALESCE(name = $1, $1 IS NULL) AND ((external_id IS NOT DISTINCT FROM $4) AND COALESCE(id > $3, true) OR COALESCE(external_id > $4, external_id IS NOT NULL)) ORDER BY external_id ASC NULLS FIRST, id ASC LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $5 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN cala_account_set_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.external_id asc nulls first, i.id asc, i.id, e.sequence
